<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>クイズ</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffe0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        h1 {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            width: 90%;
            height: 70%;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .field {
            background-color: #66cdaa;
            color: white;
            width: 40%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .field:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .field a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>僕とどこで知り合いですか？</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="field">
            <a href="/question/class">クラスルーム</a>
        </div>
        <div class="field">
            <a href="/question/massiro">まっしろ</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
